title: Olay Regenerist Deep Hydration Regenerating Cream Facial Moisturirzer 1.7 Fl Oz
Sun Self Tanning Lotion Ultra Dark Instant Tint - Dark 8oz/236ml
description: Achieve a deep, natural-looking tan for the face and body while avoiding the harmful rays of the sun with Sun Laboratories Ultra Dark Lotion. This highly moisturizing formula coats the skin in an instant dose of color to prevent streaking or patchiness. The natural active ingredient, a sugar derivative, then works deep in the skin to intensify the color over a three hour period, resulting in a rich, natural-looking hue. Its non-clogging formula is ideal for all skin types, even sensitive.

title: Sun Laboratories Dark Sunsation Self Tanning Lotion - Very Dark 8 fl oz.
description: Even a deep, dark tan is attainable without exposing your skin to the sun's harmful rays with Sun Laboratories Dark Sunsation. Formulated with a wondrous blend of natural ingredients, Dark Sunsation enhances the skin's melanin production throughout the face and body while hydrating and protecting the skin. Its nourishing formula coats the skin in instant color to prevent streaks or patches, while its sugar-based actives provide a deep, healthy tan within three hours.
